Output plots and saved model checkpoints are written here by the scripts in this directory.

  dyna_q.png              -- learning curves for n=0, 5, 50 planning steps
  world_model.png         -- training loss + k-step rollout error
  world_model.pt          -- trained world-model weights (used by model_based_planning.py)
  model_based_planning.png-- MPC vs Random episode rewards
